From 6041706b1b079c6156aff83126b20721049a0575 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: FishSlayR Dev <dev@fishslayr.local>
Date: Fri, 3 Jul 2026 02:06:28 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Port core loop to React: catch sheet, log-a-catch, push sync,
 photos, New Trip, loadouts

- CatchSheet: catch card detail view + soft-delete (tombstone, cloud+local photo cleanup)
- LogCatch: 4-step species/length/lure/details flow with photo capture and quick-rig loadouts
- Push sync: full push+pull engine (dirty tracking, last-write-wins, tombstones, first-sign-in migration)
- Photo layer: IndexedDB blob store, downscale + thumbnails, EXIF date/GPS, live geolocation, Storage upload/download
- NewTrip: full trip context form (openSessionSheet/saveSession)
- Loadouts: Tackle Box manager (5 slots, editor, delete), apply/save in catch flow, sync via profile
- Boathouse hero restored to original wording/bubbles; shared fishDisplay + refs helpers
All wording/markup carried over verbatim from the single-file app. Deferred: photo-less stubs for Edit Catch/Trip Story/Templates.
